title: 이달의소녀탐구 #123 (LOONA TV #123)
summary:
It is the beginning of Kim Lip’s era! We start off in a photo studio with unusual props.
Kim Lip’s photoshoot happens here.
0:09 -- Kim Lip: “I came here for my single album jacket shooting). She hasn’t eaten
anything for almost 5 hours.”
She continues to rant about hunger.
0:15 -- JinSoul: “We’ve lost weight too”
0:20 -- It is time for the photoshoot. (Lippie looking gorgeous here!!)
0:23 -- PD: “This is your first photoshoot?”. Lip: “Yes~!” and her photoshoot continues.
